data.description: Step inside to this spacious 4 bedroom 2 bathroom home located in the heart of Midwest City located conveniently next to Tinker Air Force Base and lots of shopping. Stepping into the backyard you are greeted with a work shed along with tons of space for hosting or those with larger pets. The house needs a little TLC but has lots of options for either a first time homeowner or someone looking for a project! Come check this one out and schedule your showing today!
